metadata.name: Salisby Dalisby’s Super Flying Bodies
metadata.description: After having a two story home in his last community built city.  Salisby came home from his office job to find his dear wife of thirty years missing no where to be found.  Two babies were also missing.  Salisby went over to his business partner and son from the same missing wife.  His son’s wife and family were also missing.  Many friends and other relatives were also abducted and missing. Salisby and son stayed in the city another month hoping to find their missing wives and family.  Later abandoned the lighted plate city to find a safer new area to make new homes.
